data.description: Welcome to your charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath home in the heart of Frankfort, KY! This delightful residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, making it an ideal place to call home.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere, with ample natural light accentuating the cozy living spaces. The well-designed floor plan seamlessly connects the living and dining areas, creating a perfect setting for both relaxation and entertainment.Step outside, and you'll discover a spacious back yard that invites endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply soaking up the Kentucky sunshine. The yard is a blank canvas for your imagination, ready to be transformed into your personal oasis. Inspections are welcome but home is being sold 'as is.'*Agents -please see agent only remarks.
